<h2>Welcome to [% sitename || 'Comserv' %]!</h2>

<p>Hello [% user.first_name || user.username || 'there' %],</p>

<p>Your account has been successfully activated. Welcome to [% sitename || 'Comserv' %]!</p>

<p><strong>Your account details:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Username:</strong> [% user.username %]</li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> [% user.email %]</li>
    [% IF user.roles %]<li><strong>Role(s):</strong> [% user.roles %]</li>[% END %]
</ul>

<p>You can now log in to your account at: <a href="[% login_url %]">[% login_url %]</a></p>

<p>From your account you can:</p>
<ul>
    <li>View and update your profile</li>
    <li>Change your password</li>
    <li>Access [% sitename || 'Comserv' %] features based on your role</li>
</ul>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact support.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The [% sitename || 'Comserv' %] Team</p>
